  schema:name "Income Statement" ;
  schema:description "An income statement — also called a profit and loss statement or P\u0026L — is a financial document that summarizes a business's revenues, costs, and expenses over a specific period. It answers a single question: did the business make or lose money during this time?" ;
  schema:datePublished "2026-03-06" ;
